&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead &amp;amp; Mentor:&lt;/strong&gt; Build and lead a small, agile team of AI engineers. Lead by example by contributing to the codebase, setting high standards for code craftsmanship, and fostering a culture of high-velocity shipping.&lt;/li&gt;
